# AI Rule Archive Skill Equivalent

- Use this workflow to catalog AI customizations without executing them.
- Store concise records in `.ai/rule-archive/catalog.jsonl`.
- Use `./scripts/catalog-agent-asset.ps1` to populate the archive.
- Use `./scripts/query-agent-archive.ps1` to query the archive.
- Track dedicated repository personas, paper personas, and their local bundles as cataloged assets rather than archivist-owned runtime skills.
- Keep coverage aligned with Copilot and Claude Code and record support in `SUPPORTED.md`.